show.description: When betrayal hides behind designer lehengas and royal smiles, one woman dares to expose it all. The Royal Sting unravels a high-stakes web of revenge, buried secrets, and power games — all under the glittering facade of a “perfect” wedding. Loyalties will break. Masks will fall. And the truth? It stings.
